Title: Coda of the Heart
Description: An ode to Micah 4:5
References:
  - Title: Micah
    Locus: 4:5
---
The prophet
says
what
God knows.
We will
one day
walk in
the word
of our
Lord,
our God,
not only
forever,
but beyond.
